  "intent": "Execute universal PCR amplification for GeneRead QIAact Lung RNA Fusion UMI Panel Kit: pre-cool temperature module to 4\u00b0C, dispense 6.6\u00b5L master mix into PCR strip tubes containing enriched DNA samples (1-12 samples), mix 7 times with 10\u00b5L volume, transfer 20\u00b5L from each tube to thermocycler plate, then run thermocycler program with 15-minute initial denaturation at 95\u00b0C, 21 cycles of 95\u00b0C for 15 seconds and 60\u00b0C for 2 minutes, followed by 72\u00b0C extension for 5 minutes and final hold at 4\u00b0C",
